name: Sparrow Creek
address: Old Furnace Rd, Boiling Springs, South Carolina 29316
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Home Designs
amenities.description: Award-winning Pulte Homes makes its Boiling Springs debut with 200 stunning new construction homes in Sparrow Creek

amenities.name: Future amenities
amenities.description: Future amenities at Sparrow Creek will include a pool, cabana, fire pit, and playground

amenities.name: tranquil Fawn
amenities.description: The tranquil Fawn Branch Creek runs through the center of the community to create a beautiful setting

amenities.name: community offers
amenities.description: The community offers convenience to I-26 and I-85 – both within a 6 to 8-minute drive of Sparrow Creek

amenities.name: Just 1.5
amenities.description: Just 1.5 miles away from Sparrow Creek, the Highway 9 corridor offers name-brand retailers and restaurants like Publix, Ingles, ALDI, Walmart, Lowes, Chick-fil-A, Dominoes, Firehouse Subs, and more

amenities.name: Sparrow Creek
amenities.description: Sparrow Creek residents can be in the walkable and inviting Downtown Spartanburg in under 20 minutes to enjoy its art galleries, music venues, museums, breweries, and restaurants like Cribb’s Kitchen on Main, The Kennedy, Skillet, FR8 Yard, and RJ Rocker Brewing

amenities.name: community’s convenience
amenities.description: The community’s convenience to North Spartanburg Sports Complex, Va-Du-Mar McMillan Park, and the picturesque Hatcher Garden and Woodland Preserve makes Sparrow Creek an ideal match for active couples and families

amenities.name: Golfers can
amenities.description: Golfers can perfect their swing and short game at the nearby Boiling Springs Golf Center, Woodfin Ridge Golf Club, Village Green Golf Club, and more

amenities.name: Sparrow Creek’s
amenities.description: Sparrow Creek’s convenience to the travel corridors at I-26 and I-85 makes commutes into the employment hubs at Spartanburg and Greenville a relative breeze
